Subject: Let's Connect About Your Application

Body:
<html><body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#222222;font-size:14px;">
<p>Hi <strong>[applicant_first_name]</strong>,</p>

<p>Thank you so much for applying for the <strong>[job_title]</strong> role at <strong>Outsourced Pro Global</strong>. We're delighted to learn more about you and to share what makes Outsourced Pro Global a great place to grow your career.</p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;">We'd love to invite you for a quick <strong>[interview_duration_text] Zoom chat</strong> with our Recruitment Specialist. This is a wonderful opportunity for us to get to know each other and explore whether this role is the right fit.</p>

<p><strong>Date:</strong> [Date]<br>
<strong>Time:</strong> [Time] [Timezone]<br>
<strong>Platform:</strong> Zoom<br>
<strong>Zoom Link:</strong> [Link]</p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;white-space:pre-line;"><strong>Meeting guests:</strong><br>[guest_list_text]</p>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><strong>Friendly Reminders:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>Kindly connect 10 minutes early to make sure your camera and microphone are working properly.</li>
<li>Use your laptop or PC for this interview.</li>
<li>Make sure that your <strong>Full Name</strong> and the <strong>role</strong> you are interviewing for are reflected in the Zoom meeting.</li>
<li>Please note that this is a formal meeting - please dress in business attire.</li>
<li>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to any of our recruiters at <strong>+61 489 275 966 (AU)</strong> or through their <strong>mobile no.</strong></li>
</ul>

<p style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;"><strong>Warm regards,</strong><br>
<strong>Recruitment Team, Outsourced Pro Global</strong></p>

[signature]
</body></html>
